==製作==
劇本由愛爾蘭編劇詹姆斯·麥法蘭負責，作為自己的首次編劇工作<ref name="variety-k3">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/pegg-hemsworth-start-kill-me-three-times-1200616204/|title=Simon Pegg, Luke Hemsworth Start ‘Kill Me Three Times’|publisher=variety.com|accessdate=2014-09-01|archive-date=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814235524/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/pegg-hemsworth-start-kill-me-three-times-1200616204/}}</ref>。電影於2013年9月在珀斯開拍。主要於西澳的多處地點取景，其中包括葡萄酒產區的瑪格​​麗特河。後期製作在維多利亞進行<ref name="variety-k3" />。

==發行==
[[File:Simon_Pegg,_Alice_Braga_&_Luke_Hemsworth_Premiere_of_Kill_Me_Three_Times_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
2014年9月，本片於[[多倫多國際電影節|多倫多國際電影節]]上首映，一個月後在英國的[[倫敦影展|倫敦影展]]發行<ref>{{cite web|title=Contemporary World Cinema » Kill Me Three Times|url=http://www.tiff.net/festivals/thefestival/programmes/contemporary-world-cinema/kill-me-three-times|publisher=[[Toronto_International_Film_Festival|Toronto International Film Festival]]|accessdate=2015-04-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414163106/http://www.tiff.net/festivals/thefestival/programmes/contemporary-world-cinema/kill-me-three-times|archivedate=2015年4月14日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Last red carpet at London film festival – in pictures|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/gallery/2014/oct/19/last-red-carpet-at-london-film-festival-in-pictures|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-04-14|date=2014-10-18|archive-date=2022-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511180157/https://www.theguardian.com/film/gallery/2014/oct/19/last-red-carpet-at-london-film-festival-in-pictures}}</ref>。在美國於2015年4月釋出在限定地區<ref>{{cite web|title=Kill Me Three Times (2015)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_me_three_times/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2015-04-14|archive-date=2022-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204044408/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_me_three_times}}</ref>。

